message: Rep. Price was born in 1967, NOT 1968. I continue to revise this page and an unauthorized user changes it back to the incorrect birthdate. Please forgo doing this. The Lottery section of this page is being removed as it is not accurate.
/* Lottery issue */ This information is false and has no legitimate source. Wikipedia is not a source.
Restored removal of sourced content. You'll need more than a bare assertion that it is "not accurate" before it can be removed. Discuss on talk page per [[WP:BRD]].
